headline: Best Buy (BBY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Since July 2024, Best Buy has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 4.1% while floating around $85.65. This is close to the S&P 500’s 7.5% gain during that period.
